OL,3,CBoy, 18, found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Cteenager at New Year's Eve fireworks
OL,6,FA jury has found an 18-year-old guilty
OL,7,Fof murder after a 16-year-old boy was
OL,8,Fstabbed at a New Year's Eve event.
OL,10,FAreece Lloyd-Hall attacked Harry
OL,11,FPitman in front of revellers who had
OL,12,Fgathered on London's Primrose Hill to
OL,13,Fwatch fireworks over the River Thames
OL,14,Fon December 31 2023.
OL,16,FHarry and Lloyd-Hall were strangers to
OL,17,Feach other and had gone to Primrose
OL,18,FHill with separate groups of friends.
