OL,4,Cteenager at New Year's Eve fireworks
OL,6,F"Lively and boisterous" Harry Pitman
OL,7,Fhad been playfighting before he was
OL,8,Fattacked by Areece Lloyd-Hall.
OL,10,FLloyd-Hall, now aged 18, pushed
OL,11,Fforward and lunged at Harry with a
OL,12,Fpointed dagger, metres from where
OL,13,Funiformed police officers were
OL,14,Fstationed.
OL,16,FIn "shocking" mobile phone footage
OL,17,Fplayed in court, a knife sheath is
OL,18,Fseen to fly through the air during the
OL,19,Ffast-paced incident.
