OL,6,FHarry holds his neck, his white T-
OL,7,Fshirt covered in blood, as he pushes
OL,8,Fthrough crowds calling to officers for
OL,9,F"help".
OL,11,FHe collapsed and died minutes later,
OL,12,Fshortly before midnight.
OL,14,FCollege student Lloyd-Hall, who was 16
OL,15,Fat the time, claimed he thought he had
OL,16,Fonly hit Harry with the sheath in an
OL,17,Fattempt to get Harry away from him.
OL,19,FHe said: "I did not want him to lose
OL,20,Fhis life.
