OL,6,F"I feel horrible for what I caused. It
OL,7,Fwas not my intention."
OL,9,FHe said he ran off not realising what
OL,10,Fhad happened because he was holding a
OL,11,Fknife and knew there were police
OL,12,Fofficers nearby.
OL,14,FJurors were told Lloyd-Hall was
OL,15,Fsuffering from cannabis-induced
OL,16,Fparanoia and may have suffered post-
OL,17,Ftraumatic stress disorder triggered by
OL,18,Fwitnessing the aftermath of an earlier
OL,19,Fstabbing and the loss of a friend to
OL,20,Fknife crime in June 2023.
