OL,3,CBoy, 18, found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Cteenager at New Year's Eve fireworks
OL,6,FAfter a retrial at the Old Bailey,
OL,7,FLloyd-Hall, from Westminster, was
OL,8,Ffound guilty of murder by a majority
OL,9,Fof 11 to one after a jury deliberated
OL,10,Ffor nearly eight hours.
OL,12,FAt a trial in October last year, a
OL,13,Fjury found Lloyd-Hall guilty of
OL,14,Fpossession of an offensive weapon but
OL,15,Ffailed to agree on other charges, it
OL,16,Fcan now be reported.
OL,18,FThere were gasps from Harry's family
OL,19,Fsitting in court as Lloyd-Hall was
OL,20,Fconvicted of murder.
