OL,6,FEarlier in the evening special
OL,7,Fconstable David Smith said Harry
OL,8,Fseemed excitable and had "physically
OL,9,Fbounced" up to him to engage in
OL,10,Ffriendly chat.
OL,12,FHe went on to "fist bump" another man
OL,13,Fwho had gone to watch the fireworks
OL,14,Fwith his family.
OL,16,FThe fatal incident appeared to have
OL,17,Fbeen sparked by a scuffle between
OL,18,FHarry and one of the defendant's
OL,19,Ffriends shortly after 11.30pm.
