OL,6,FPlayfighting, Harry lost his balance
OL,7,Fwhile seeing how high he could kick
OL,8,Fand bumped into the boy standing
OL,9,Fbehind.
OL,11,FIn return, Harry was shoved and
OL,12,Fslapped on the back of the head,
OL,13,Fcausing him to say: "Don't touch me,
OL,14,Fbecause I didn't touch you."
OL,16,FLloyd-Hall pushed his way towards
OL,17,FHarry, holding his trousers and
OL,18,Fsaying: "Wot wot wot wot wot."
