OL,6,FIn mobile phone footage, a girl warns
OL,7,F"mindi", the Somalian word for knife,
OL,8,Fas the defendant produces a blade from
OL,9,Fhis waistband.
OL,11,FHarry can be seen swinging a punch
OL,12,Fbefore Lloyd-Hall swings the knife
OL,13,Fupwards in an arc and down on to
OL,14,FHarry's neck.
OL,16,FPolice body-worn camera footage shows
OL,17,FHarry moving through the crowd seeking
OL,18,Fhelp before he collapsed.
OL,20,FThe defendant made off, discarding the
OL,21,Fknife, his clothes and mobile phone.
