OL,6,FThe knife scabbard was left at the
OL,7,Fscene and was found to have the
OL,8,Fdefendant's DNA on it.
OL,10,FAfter a media appeal, Lloyd-Hall went
OL,11,Fto Hammersmith police station with his
OL,12,Ffather on January 4 2024.
OL,14,FThe court was told the defendant had
OL,15,Fno previous convictions and had been
OL,16,Fdiagnosed with attention deficit
OL,17,Fhyperactivity disorder.
